# {{name}} CLI

A command-line interface built with the [Fathym CLI](https://jsr.io/@fathym/cli) framework.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Run a command in development mode
ftm run hello

# Run with arguments and flags
ftm run hello Alice --loud

# Run intent tests
ftm test

# Build and compile to native binary
ftm build && ftm compile

# Install to PATH
ftm install --useHome
```

## Project Structure

```
./
├── .cli.json           # CLI identity (Name, Tokens, Version)
├── .cli.init.ts        # IoC service registration
├── deno.jsonc          # Deno configuration and tasks
├── commands/           # Command implementations
│   ├── hello.ts        # Fluent API example
│   └── wave.ts         # Class-based example
└── intents/            # Intent test files
    ├── .intents.ts     # Test entry point
    ├── hello.intents.ts
    └── wave.intents.ts
```

## Available Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `hello [name]` | Prints a friendly greeting |
| `wave [target]` | Waves at a friend with optional excitement |

